snippet.title: Celeste releasing January 2018
snippet.description:
From the creators of TowerFall, Celeste is a hardcore mountain-climbing platformer coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, XBox One, and Steam in January 2018! 

http://www.celestegame.com

Trailer by Kert Gartner, Power Up Audio, and Lena Chappelle.
